hadiths[114]{hadithnumber,text}:
3436,"Hazrat Usama bin Shareek (Saalbi) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main (majlis mein) mojud tha jab Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawalat kar rahey they : kya falan kaam karney mein hum par gunah hai? kya falan kaam karney mein hum par gunah hai? to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : Allah key bando ! Allah ney harj (tangi) ko door kar diya hai magar jisney apney bhai ki izzat mein sey eik hissa kaat liya, yehi hai jisney gunah kiya. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya hamein is baat sey gunah hoga ke hum (bimari sey shifa key liye) dawaa (istimal) na keren? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key bando ! (shifa key liye) dawaa (istimal) kiya karo, Allah Subhaan-o-Ta'alaa ney jo bimari banai hai, uski shifa (key liye dawaa) bhi banai hai, siwaye shadeed budhapey key. unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! bandey ko sab sey behtar chiz kya ata hui hai? farmaya : achchha akhlaq."
3437,"Hazrat Abu Khuzaama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya gaya : hum dawaaon key zariey sey ilaj kartey hain, aur duaon key sath dam kartey hain, aur difaai ashiya (cheezon) key zariey sey apna bachao kartey hain, kya ye cheezen Allah ki taqdir mein sey kisi chiz ko rok sakti hain? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye bhi Allah ki taqdir mein shamil hain."
3438,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ney jo bimari nazil ki hai, uski dawaa bhi zarur nazil ki hai."
3439,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ney jo bimari nazil ki hai, uski shifa (dawaa) bhi nazil ki hai."
3440,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ki iyaadat farmaai to us sey puchha : tumhen kis chiz ki khahish hai? usney kaha : gehun ki roti ko ji chahta hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis key paas gehun ki roti ho wo apney bhai key yahan bhej dey. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi ka mareez kisi chiz ki khahish zahir karey to usey chahiye ke wo isey khila dey."
3441,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik bimar ki iyaadat key liye uskey paas tashrif ley gaey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tumhen kisi chiz ki khahish hai? kya tumhara ji ka'ak khaney ko chahta hai? usney kaha : haan, chunanche uskey liye ka'ak mangwaayaa gaya."
3442,"Hazrat Umme Munzir Sulami binte Qais Ansaariya (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye. aap key sath Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bimari ki wajeh sey kamzor ho gaey they. hamarey yahan neem pukhta (adhpaki) khajuron key khoshey (rassi sey) latak rahey they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un mein sey ley ley kar (khajuren) kha rahey they ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi khaney key liye kuchh kajhoorein ley lein. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ali ! ruk jao. tum abhi (bimari sey uthey ho), isliye kamzor ho. Umme Munzir (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye chukandar aur jau pakaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ali ! is mein sey khao, ye tumharey liye ziyada mufeed hai."
3443,"Hazrat Suheb (bin Sanan) Romi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa jabkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney roti aur khajuren thin. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aaiye ! tanaawul kijiye. mainey khajuren khana shuru kar den. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum khajuren kha rahey ho, halanke tumhari aankh dukhti hai. mainey kaha : main dusri taraf sey chabaa raha hun. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) muskura diye."
3444,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney mareezon ko khaney peeney par majbur na kiya karo, unhen Allah Taala khilata aur pilata hai."
3445,"Ummul-momineen Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ghar mein jab kisi ko bukhar hota to aap talbeena tayyar karney ka hukm detey. aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : is sey ghamzada insan key dil ko sahara milta hai. aur bimar key dil sey ranj ko is tarah door karta hai jis tarah koi aurat pani key zariey sey apney chehrey sey mail kuchail door karti hai."
3446,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : naa-pasandida mufeed chiz talbeena (hareera) ko apnao. Ummul-mominin‬ (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ghar mein jab koi bimar ho jata to (hareere ki) handiyaa aag par chadhi rehti yahan tak key (uska maamla) kisi eik taraf lag jata, yani wo faut ho jata ya shifa yaab."
3447,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kaley daney mein saam key siwa har marz ki shifa hai. saam ka matlab maut hai, aur kaalaa dana kalonji hai."
3448,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is kalay daney (kalonji) ko ikhtiyar karo. is mein maut key siwa har marz ki shifa hai."
3449,"Hazrat Khalid bin Saad (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : hum log safar mein they. hamarey sath Hazrat Ghalib bin Abjar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. wo raastey mein bimar ho gaey. hum log Madina pahunchey to wo (us waqt bhi) bimar they. Hazrat ibne-Abi Ateeq (Rahimahullah) (Abdullah bin Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Bakr) un ki bimar pursi key liye aaye to hum sey farmaya : tum ye kaalaa dana (kalonji) istimal karo. uskey paanch saat daney ley kar pees lo, phir zaitun key tel mein mila kar in ki naak mein chand qatrey is taraf aur chand qatrey is taraf (nathnon mein) dalo kyonkey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : ye kaalaa dana har bimari ki shifa hai, siwaye iskey ke saam (hi muqaddar) ho. mainey kaha : saam kya hai? unhoney farmaya : maut."
3450,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs mahiney mein teen din subh key waqt shehad chaat ley , usey koi badi aafat ( bimari) nahin aayegi ."
3451,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein shehad ka hadiya pesh kya gaya . aap ney hamarey darmiyan eik eik chammach shehad taqseem farmaya. mainey apna hissa ley liya, phir arz kya : Allah key Rasool! mazeed eik chammach ley lun? farmaya : haan (ley lo.)"
3452,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : do shifa wali cheezen ikhtiyar karo : shehad aur Quran."
3453,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri aur Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khumbi man ki qism sey hai. uska pani aankh key liye shifa hai. ajwa khajoor jannat sey hai aur ye jinkey asar (ya junun) sey shifa deti hai. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney Saeed bin Muslima bin Hisham key wastey sey bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey mazkura baala riwayat ki misl bayan ki hai."
3454,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid bin Amr bin Nufel (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khumbi us man sey hai jo Allah ney Bani-Israel par nazil kya tha. aur uska pani aankh key liye shifa hai."
3455,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki majlis mein baat cheet kar rahey they ke khumbi ka zikr aa gaya. baaz hazraat ney kaha : ye to zamin ki chechak hai. ye baat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz ki gaee to aap ney farmaya : khumbii man (ki qismon mein) sey (eik qism) hai. aur ajwa khajoor jannat sey hai aur wo zahar sey shifa hai."
3456,"Hazrat Raafey bin Amr Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna . ajwa aur sakhra jannat sey (aaye) hain. Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mainey sakhra ka lafz khud apney ustaad (Mashmail bin Ayas Muzni (Rahimahullah)) key munh sey suna hai."
3457,"Hazrat Abu-Abi Abdullah bin Umme haram (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein dono qiblon ki taraf namaz padhi hai. unhoney bayan kya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap ney farmaya : suna aur sanut apnao, un mein saam (maut) key siwa har bimari sey shifa hai. arz kya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! saam kya hai? aap ney farmaya : maut . ibne-Abi abla (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : sanut sey murad shabt (khushbudar pattey jo khaney mein daley jatey hain) hai. doosrey hazraat kehtey hain ke us sey murad wo shehad hai jo ghi ki mashkon mein rakha gaya ho. eik shayer ka sher hai : wo log shehad miley ghi ki tarah hain, wo khayanat nahin kartey (ya aapas mein nahin ladtey) aur apney hamsaaey ki hifazat kartey hain taake usey dhoka na diya jaey."
3458,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do-pahar key waqt (zohar ki namaz key awwal waqt mein, masjid mein) tashrif ley gaey. main bhi awwal waqt (masjid mein) chala gaya. mainey (nafl) namaz padhi, phir beth gaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : kya terey pet mein dard hai? mainey kaha : ji haan, aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : uth kar namaz padh kyonkey namaz mein shifa hai. eik riwayat mein hai ke aap ney Faarsi mein kaha : kya terey pet mein dard hai? Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : eik aadmi ney ye hadees apney khandan walon ko sunai to unhoney ( qazi sey) uski shikayat kar di. (hadees key zaeef honey ki taraf ishara hai.)"
3459,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney buri dawa sey mana farmaya hai. us sey murad zahar hai."
3460,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney zahar pi kar khud kushi kar li, wo jahannam mein hamesha hamesha zahar peeta rahega."
3461,"Hazrat Asma bint Umes (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : tum kon si chiz sey julab leti ho? mein kaha : shabram sey. aap ney farmaya : ye to bahut garm hai. phir mainey us maqsad key liye suna makki istimal ki to aap ney farmaya : agar koi chiz maut sey bacha sakti to wo sana hoti . aur sana maut sey shifa hai."
3462,"Hazrat Umme Qais (Aamna) binte-Mohsin (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main apney eik bachey ko ley kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui. usko galey pad gaey they aur mainey unhen ungli sey dabaaya tha (jo us bimari ka raaij ilaj tha. (Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum is bimari ka ilaj bachon ka gala ungli sey daba kar kyon karti ho? ud hindi istimal kya karo. is mein saat shifaaein hain. galey pad janey ki surat mein naak mein tapkaya jaey zaatul-janb ki surat mein pilaya jaey. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney eik dusri sanad sey bhi ye riwayat sabiqa hadees key hum-maani Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan ki hai. riwayat key Raavi Yunus ney kaha : ( أَعْلَقْتُ ) key maana ( غَمَزْتُ ) yani ungli sey dabaaney key hain."
3463,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : arqun-Nisa ka ilaj ye hai ke jangli bhed (ya jangli dunbey) ki chakti ko ley kar pighla liya jaey, phir uskey teen hissey kar liye jaeyn, phir rozaana eik hissa Nihar munh pi liya jaey."
3464,"Hazrat Suhel bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jange-Uhud key din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) zakhmi ho gaey. aapka samney waley daanton key sath wala daant toot gaya. aap key sar mein khod toot kar ghus gaya. Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aap key jism Mubarak sey khoon ko dho kar saaf karney lagen aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) dhaal mein pani la kar dal rahey they. jab Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney dekha ke pani dalney sey khoon aur ziyada behta hai to unhoney eik chataai ka takra ley kar jalaaya. jab uski raakh bin gaee to wo zakham par laga di tab khoon ruk gaya."
3465,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey malum hai ke jange-Uhad key moqey par kis ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key chehra Mubarak ko zakhmi kya. aur kon Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key chehra Mubarak key zakham ka khoon band kar raha tha aur zakham ka ilaj kar raha tha. aur kon dhaal mein pani la raha tha. aur zakham ka ilaj kis chiz sey kya gaya ke khoon band ho gaya . phir farmaya : dhaal mein pani to Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) la rahey they. aur zakhmon ka ilaj Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) kar rahi thin . jab khoon band na huwa to Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney purani chataai ka eik tukda ley kar uski raakh zakham par rakhi to zakham sey khoon ruk gaya."
3466,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs ilaj kerey. halanke is sey pehley wo tabeeb key tor par maroof nahin to wo zimmedar hai."
3467,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Zatul-Janb (pasli key dard) ka ilaj ye tajwiz farmaya ke waras, aud hindi aur zaitun key tel ka Ladud kya jaey."
3468,"Hazrat Umme Qais ( aamna ( bint Mohsin (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ud hindi (ilaj key liye) ikhtiyar karo. is mein saat shifaein hain (saat marzon ki shifa hai) un mein sey eik (bimari) zaatul-Janb hai. ibne-Samaan ney apni riwayat mein bayan kya hai ke ud hindi mein saat bimariyon ki shifa hai. un mein sey eik (bimari) zaatul-janb hai."
3469,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki majlis mein bukhar ka zikr huwa to eik aadmi ney isey bura bhala kaha . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is (bukhaar) ko bura na kaho. us sey gunah is tarah door ho jatey hain jis tarah aag sey lohey ki mail kuchail door ho jati hai."
3470,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik bimar ki iyaadat key liye tashrif ley gaey jisey bukhar tha. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bhi sath they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ( mareez sey) farmaya : khush ho jao ! Allah Taala farmata hai : bukhar meri aag hai jisey mein duniya mein apney momin bandey par musallat karta hun taake aakhirat mein jahannam key azab key iwaz uska hissa us ( bukhaar) ko qarar diya jaey.
3471,"ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bukhar jahannam ki bhap sey hai, lihaza usey pani key zariey sey thanda karo."
3472,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bukhar ki shiddat jahannam ki bhap mein sey (eik qism) hai, lihaza usey pani key zariey sey thanda karo."
3473,"Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye farman suna : bukhar jahannam ki bhap sey hai, lihaza usey pani key zariey sey thanda karo. phir aap Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) key eik betey key paas tashrif ley gaey aur farmaya : ( اكْشِفِ الْبَاسْ , رَبَّ النَّاسْ , إِلَهَ النَّاسْ ) takleef door kar dey, aey logon key Malik! aey logon key mabood!"
3474,"Hazrat Asma bint Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke jab kisi bukhar wali aurat ko unkey paas laya jata to wo pani talab farmaatin aur usey us (mareez aurat) key gireban mein dal detin, aur farmaati thin : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : usey pani key zariey sey thanda karo. aur farmaya hai : ye jahannam ki bhap mein sey hai."
3475,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bukhar jahannam ki eik dhonkni hai. usey thandey pani key zariey sey door hataao."
3476,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jin chizon sey tum ilaj kartey ho, agar un mein sey kisi mein koi bhalai (aur faeyda) hai to wo seengi (laganey mein) hai."
3477,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis raat mujhey sair karaai gaee (aur Meraj hui) main farishton ki jis jamaat key paas sey guzra, wo sab mujhey yehi kehtey rahey : Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) seengi lagwaaya karen."
3478,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : seengi laganey wala achcha banda hai. khoon ley jata hai, kamar ko halka karta hai aur beenai ko tez karta hai."
3479,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis raat mujhey Israa (aur Meraj) hui, main (farishton ki) jis jamaat key paas sey guzraa, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni ummat ko seengi lagwaaney ka hukm dijiye."
3480,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey seengi lagwaaney ki ijazat talab ki to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney abu-Taiba (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke unhen seengi laga den. Raavi bayan kartey hain : merey khayal mein abu-Taiba (Raziallahu anhu) ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) key razaai (doodh sharik) bhai they, ya na-baligh ladkey they."
3481,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin Malik) ibn Buhena (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Lahi jamal key maqam par ehraam ki haalat mein sar key darmiyan (taalu mein) seengi lagwaai."
3482,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Jibril (Alaihissalam) ney nazil ho kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko gardan ki ragon par aur dono kandhon key darmiyan (gardan key qarib) seengii lagwaaney ki hidayat ki."
3483,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney gardan ki ragon par aur dono kandhon key darmiyan seengi lagwai.
3484,"Hazrat abu-Kabsha (Saeed bin Amr Anmari) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sar par aur kandhon key darmiyan seengi lagwatey they aur farmatey they : jo shakhs apney jism sey is tarah (seengi lagwa kar) khoon nikalwata hai, wo agar kisi bimari ka koi aur ilaj na karey to koi nuqsan nahin."
3485,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghodey sey khajoor key darkht key (katey huye) taney par gir padey, us sey aap key paon ka jod mutassir ho gaya. Imam Wakee (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : hadees ka matlab ye hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney takleef ki wajeh sey paon par seengi lagwaai."
3486,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs seengi lagwana chahey, usey chahiye ke) chaand ki satrah, unnis ya ikkis taareekh ko seengi lagwaaney ki koshish kerey. aisa na ho ke dorane-khoon mein khalal waqey ho aur wafat ho jaey ."
3487,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Hazrat Nafey (Rahimahullah) sey farmaya : merey khoon mein josh (aur haraarat) ki keyfiyat paida ho gaee hai, lihaza merey liye seengi laganey wala talash karo . ho sakey to naram mizaj aadmi lana, aur bahut boodha ya bahut kam umr na lana. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai, aap ney farmaya : nihar munh seengi lagwana ziyada mufid hai. is mein shifa aur barkat hai. us sey aql aur hafzey mein taraqqi hoti hai, isliye Allah ka naam ley kar Jumerat ko seengi lagwa liya karo. buddh, Juma, hafta aur itwaar ko ehtimam sey seengi lagwaaney sey perhez karo. peer aur mangal key din seengi lagwaya liya karo . Allah Taala ney Hazrat Ayub (Alaihissalam) ko bimari sey isi din shifa di thi. aur aap (Alaihissalam) ki aazmaaish (aur bimari) buddh sey shuru ki thi. kodh aur phalbhari ka marz sirf buddh key din ya buddh ki raat ko zahir hota hai."
3488,"Hazrat Nafey (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : Nafey ! merey khoon mein josh paida ho gaya hai, lihaza merey paas seengi laganey wala lao . jawan aadmi lana , boodha ya bacha na lana . Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap ney farmaya : nihar munh seengi lagwana ziyada mufid hai, us sey aql badhti hai, aur hafiza ziyada hota hai, aur achi yaddaasht waley ki yaddaasht bhi ziyada ho jati hai. to jisney seengi lagwani ho wo Allah ka naam ley kar Jumerat ko lagwa ley. Juma, hafta aur itwaar ko seengi lagwaaney sey ijtinab karo. somwar aur mangal ko seengi lagwa liya karo . aur buddh ko bhi seengi lagwaaney sey perhez karo kyonkey Hazrat Ayub (Alaihissalam) ko isi din aazmaaish (aur bimari) aai thi. juzaam aur baras sirf buddh key din ya buddh ki raat ko zahir hota hai."
3489,"Hazrat Aqqar (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney khud ko daagha, ya dam karwaya, wo tawakkul sey mehroom ho gaya."
3490,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney daaghney sey mana farmaya : mainey khud ko daaghaa to mujhey faeyda na huwa aur main kamiyab na huwa."
3491,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shifa teen chizon mein hai : shehad peeney mein, seengi key zakham mein aur aag key sath daaghney mein. aur main apni ummat ko daaghney sey mana karta hun."
3492,Hazrat Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman bin Saad bin Zarara Ansari apney chacha Yahyaa bin Saad bin Zarara sey riwayat bayan kartey hain ke Muhammad (Rahimahullah) key nana Hazrat Saad bin Zarara (Raziallahu anhu) ko halaq mein dard huwa jisey zibeh kehtey hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main Abu-Umama (Saad bin Zarara (Raziallahu anhu)) key ilaj ki puri koshish karunga yahan tak key maamla merey bas sey bahar ho jaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen apney haath sey daaghaa lekin wo (jaan bar na ho sakey aur) faut ho gaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : yahudiyon ko buri maut nasib ho ! wo kehtey hain : is (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam))  ney apney sathi ki jaan kyon na bacha li? main to iskey liye ya apney liye (Allah key faisley key muqabley mein) kuchh ikhtiyar nahin rakhta.
3493,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) bimar ho gaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey paas eik tabeeb bheja. usney un ki rag akhal par daagh diya."
3494,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki rag akhal ko do baar daaghaa tha.
3495,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : asmad surma (aakhon mein lagana) apney ooper lazim kar lo kyonkey wo nazar ko tez karta aur (palkon) key baal ugata hai."
3496,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sotey waqt asmad surma (aakhon mein lagana) zaruri samajh lo kyonkey wo nazar ko tez karta aur (palkon key) baal ugata hai."
3497,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara behtareen surma asmad hai. wo nazar ko tez karta aur (palkon ke) baal ugata hai."
3498,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo surma lagaey, wo taaq (eik ya teen baar) lagaey, jisney ye kaam kya, usney achchha kiya. aur jisney na kiya, is par koi harj nahin."
3499,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki eik surmey daani thi. aap us sey har aankh mein teen baar surma lagatey they."
3500,"Hazrat Tariq bin Suwed Hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamarey ilaqey mein angoor hotey hain, hum unhen nichodtey (aur unkey ras sey sharab banatey) hain, hum usey pi liya keren? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin. mainey dobara sawal kartey huye arz kiya : hum us (sharab) key sath bimar ka ilaj kartey hain. (kya ye jayez hai)? aap ney farmaya : wo shifa nahin balke wo to khud eik bimari hai."
3501,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : behtareen dawaa Quran hai."
3502,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki azad karda khaadima Hazrat Umme Raafey Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab bhi koi zakham aa jata ya kaanta chubh jata to aap is par mehndi lagatey."
3503,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke qabila Urena key kuch afrad Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye . unhen Madina Munawra ki aab o huwa muwaafiq na aai, chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : agar tum hamarey oonton key rewad mein chaley jao aur unka doodh aur peshab piyo (to sehat yaab ho jaogey.) chunanche unhoney aisey hi kya."
3504,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : makkhi key eik par mein zahar aur doosrey mein shifa hai. jab wo khaney (ya peeney) ki chiz mein gir padey to usey is mein dubo do, (phir nikal kar phenk do) kyonkey wo zahar (wala par) aagey aur shifa (wala par) peechey rakhti hai."
3505,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tumharey (kisi key) mashrub mein makkhi gir padey to usey chahiye ke is mein dubo dey, phir (bahir nikal kar) phenk dey kyonkey uskey eik par mein bimari aur doosrey mein shifa hai."
3506,"Hazrat Aamir bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nazar ka lagna eik haqiqat hai."
3507,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nazar ka lagna haq hai."
3508,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (nazar sey) Allah ki panah maango kyonkey nazar ka lagna eik haqiqat hai."
3509,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Asad) bin Sehal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat Sehal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) nahaa rahey they ke Hazrat Aamir bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) guzrey, unhoney (Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekh kar) kaha : jaisa (khush rang jism) aaj dekha hai, (pehley) kabhi nahin dekha. kisi parda nasheen (kanwari ladki) ki jild bhi aeisi (khush rang) nahin (hoti). wo fauran hi zamin par gir padey (achchha tez bukhar huwa ke khadey na reh sakey). unhen Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas laaya gaya aur kaha gaya : Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ki khabar lijiye, wo to gir padey hain (uth bhi nahin saktey). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhen iskey barey mein kis par shak hai? logon ney kaha : Aamir bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) (ki nazar lagi hai). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya wajeh hai ke eik aadmi apney bhai ko qatl karney wali harkat karta hai? agar kisi ko apney bhai ki koi chiz nazar aaye jo usey achchhi lagey to usey chahiye ke usey barkat ki dua dey. phir pani talab farmaya aur Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke wuzu karen, chunanche unhoney apna chehra, kohniyon tak, dono haath , dono ghutney , aur tehband ka andar ka hissa dhoya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wo pani Sehal par dalney ka hukm diya. Sufiyan ney kaha : Maamar ney Imam Zohri sey bayan kiya : aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya ke wo bartan un (Sehal) key peechhey sey (un par) undel diya jaaey."
3510,"Hazrat Ubaid bin Rifaa Zarqi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) key beton ko nazar lag jati hai, main unhen dam karwa liya karun? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan, agar koi chiz taqdir ka muqabla kar sakti to nazar us (taqdir) sey aagey badh jati."
3511,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jinnon aur insanon ki nazar sey panah milney ki dua kiya kartey they. jab muawwizatain (Sura-Falaq aur Sura-Naas) nazil huin to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney inhen ikhtiyar farma liya aur in key ilawa dusri cheezen chhod den."
3512,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen nazar ka dam karwaaney ka hukm diya.
3513,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dam to sirf nazar sey ya dank maarney wali chiz (bichchhu waghera key dasney ki wajeh) sey hota hai."
3514,"Hazrat abu-Bakar bin Muhammad (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, ke Hazrat Khalida binte-Anas Umme bani Hazam Saaidiya (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur aapko kuch dam sunaiye (aur daryaft kya ke ye jayez hain ya nahin?) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen unkey sath dam karney ka hukm diya."
3515,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Ansaar ka eik gharanaa, jinhen aale Amr bin Hazam kaha jata tha, (bichchhu waghera key) dank ka dam kartey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dam karney sey mana farma diya. unhoney khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney dam jhaadu sey mana farma diya hai, halanke hum zehreeley janwer key dank ka dam kiya kartey hain, aap ney farmaya : mujhey sunao. unhoney dam key alfaz sunaaey to aap ney farmaya : in mein koi harj nahin. ye to iqrar hain."
3516,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (zehreeli chizon key) dank ka, nazar ka aur namla ka dam karney ki ijazat di hai."
3517,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney sanp aur bichchhu key dam ki ijazat di hai."
3518,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi ko bichchhu ney dank maara to wo raat bhar so na saka. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya gaya ke falan ko bichchhu ney dank maara to usey raat bhar neend nahin aai. aap ney farmaya : agar wo Sham ko ye dua padh leta to usey subah tak bichchhu key dank ki takleef na uthaani padti. (أَعُوذُ بِكَلِمَاتِ اللَّهِ التَّامَّاتِ مِنْ شَرِّ ما خَلَقَ),''main Allah key kamil (be-nuqs aur be-aeb) kalimaat key zariey sey (Allah ki) panah mein aata hun, har us chiz key shar sey jo usney paida ki hai."""
3519,"Hazrat Amr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sanp key kaatey ka eik dam sunaya, ya aap ko sanp key kaatey ka eik dam sunaya gaya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey padhney (aur mareez par dam kerney) ka hukm diya."
3520,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi bimar key paas tashrif ley jatey aur uskey liye dua kartey to farmatey : (أَذْهِبِ الْبَأْسَ رَبَّ النَّاسِ , وَاشْفِ أَنْتَ الشَّافِي , اشْفِ شِفَاءً لَا يُغَادِرُ سَقَمًا), ''bimari door kar dey, aey logon key Rab ! aur shifa ata farma, to hi shifa deney wala hai, teri shifa key siwa koi shifa nahin, aisi shifa dey ke bimari ko bilkul na rehney dey.''"
3521,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mareez ki shifa-yaabi key liye ungli par luaabe-dahan laga kar yun kehtey they : ( بِسْمِ اللَّهِ تُرْبَةُ أَرْضِنَا بِرِيقَةِ بَعْضِنَا يُشْفَى سَقِيمُنَا بِإِذْنِ رَبِّنَا ) Allah key naam sey, hamari zamin ki mitti, hum mein sey baaz key luaab dahan sey mil kar, hamarey rab key hukm sey, hamarey mariz ki shifa yaabi ka zaria hogi ."
3522,"Hazrat Usman bin abul-Aas Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa . mujhey itna ( shadeed) dard ho raha tha ke main mara ja raha tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : apna daayan haath dard key maqam par rakh kar saat baar keh : ( بِسْمِ اللَّهِ أَعُوذُ بِعِزَّةِ اللَّهِ وَقُدْرَتِهِ مِنْ شَرِّ ما أَجِدُ سَبْعَ مَرَّاتٍ ) Allah key naam sey , main Allah ki azmat o qudrat ki panah mein aata hun us burai sey jo main paata hun aur jis sey darta hun . mainey ye dua ( is tarah) padhi to Allah Taala ney mujhey shifa dey di."
3523,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Jibril (Alaihissalam) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein tashrif laye aur farmaya : aey Muhammad! aap bimar ho gaey hain? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan. Jibril (Alaihissalam) ney farmaya : ( بِسْمِ اللَّهِ أَرْقِيكَ , وَاللَّهُ يَشْفِيكَ , مِنْ كُلِّ شَيْءٍ يُؤْذِيكَ , وَمَنْ كُلِّ عَيْنٍ وَحَاسِدٍ , اللَّهُ يَشْفِيكَ , بِسْمِ اللَّهِ أَرْقِيكَ ) main aap ko Allah key naam sey dam karta hun, aap ko taklif deney wali har chiz sey, har jaan ya aankh ya haasid key shar sey, Allah aap ko shifa dey. main aap ko Allah key naam sey dam karta hun."
3524,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri iyaadat key liye tashrif laye aur mujh sey farmaya : kya main tujhey wo dam na karun jo merey paas Jibril (Alaihissalam) laye hain? mainey kaha : kyon nahin, aey Allah key Rasool! merey maa baap aap par qurban hun . aap ney teen baar farmaya : ( بِسْمِ اللهِ أَرْقِيكَ , وَاللهُ يَشْفِيكَ مِنْ كُلِّ دَاءٍ يُؤْذِيكَ , وَمِنْ شَرِّ النَّفَّاثَاتِ فِي الْعُقَدِ , وَمِنْ شَرِّ حَاسِدٍ إِذَا حَسَدَ ) Allah key naam sey tujhey dam karta hun, aur Allah tujhey shifa dega , tujh mein mojud har bimari sey , girahon mein phunkein maarney waaliyon key shar sey aur hasad karney waley key shar sey jab wo hasad kerey."
3525,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Hasan aur Hazrat Husain (Raziallahu anhuma) ko dam kartey to yun farmatey they : ( أَعُوذُ بِكَلِمَاتِ اللَّهِ التَّامَّةِ مِنْ كُلِّ شَيْطَانٍ وَهَامَّةٍ , وَمِنْ كُلِّ عَيْنٍ لَامَّةٍ ) main Allah Taala key kamil kalmaat ki panah mein aata hun, har shetan sey aur keedey makodey sey aur har deewana kar deney wali aankh sey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hamarey dada Hazrat Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ye dua padh kar Ismail aur Is-haq alaihimussalam ko ya farmaya : Ismail aur Yaqub alehissalam ko dam kya kartey they. aur ye hadees Imam Wakee (Rahimahullah) ki hai."
3526,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bukhar aur har qism key dard sey) shifa key liye (ye dua sikhaya kartey they ke yun kahin : ( بِسْمِ اللهِ الْكَبِيرِ , أَعُوذُ بِاللهِ الْعَظِيمِ , مِنْ شَرِّ عِرْقٍ نَعَّارٍ , وَمِنْ شَرِّ حَرِّ النَّارِ ) kibriyaai waley Allah key naam sey , main azmat waley Allah ki panah mein aata hun, josh maarti rag key shar sey aur aag ki garmi key shar sey . riwayat key Raavi abu-Aamir (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : main logon sey us riwayat key alfaz mein ikhtilaf karta hun, main ( « نعار » ki bajaey ( « یعار » kehta hun . eik dusri sanad sey us riwayat mein ye lafz marvi hain : (مِنْ شَرِّ عِرْقٍ یَعَّار) phadakti rag key shar sey ."
3527,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bukhar tha. Jibril (Alaihissalam) tashrif laye aur farmaya : ( بِسْمِ اللَّهِ أَرْقِيكَ , مِنْ كُلِّ شَيْءٍ يُؤْذِيكَ , مِنْ حَسَدِ حَاسِدٍ وَمِنْ كُلِّ عَيْنٍ , اللَّهُ يَشْفِيكَ) mein aap ko Allah key naam sey dam karta hun, har us chiz sey jo aap ko takleef deti hai, hasad karney waley key hasad sey aur har aankh sey , Allah aap ko shifa dey."
3528,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dam kartey waqt phunk maartey they.
3529,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab bimar ho jatey they to muawwizat suraten padh kar apney aap par phunk maartay they. jab aap ka marz shiddat ikhtiyar kar gaya to main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par) ye suratein (padhti thi, aur aap ka haath us sey barkat ki ummid par (aap key jism par) pherti thi ."
3530,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya Hazrat Zenab (bint Muawiya Saqfiya) (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamarey yahan eik budhiya aaya karti thi. wo surkh baad ka dam kya karti thi. aur hamarey paas lambey paayon wali eik chaarpai thi. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) jab ghar mein dakhil hotey to (pehley) khaanstey aur aawaz detey (phir andar dakhil hotey.) eik din wo tashrif laye . jab us (budhiya) ney unki aawaz suni to un sey parda kar liya. wo aa kar merey paas beth gaey. unhoney mujhey haath lagaya to unhen dhaga mehsus huwa (jo mainey galey mein dala huwa tha.) unhoney kaha : ye kya hai? mainey kaha is mein mujhey surkhbaad ka dam kar key diya gaya hai. unhoney usey khinch liya aur tod kar phenk diya . aur farmaya : Abdullah key ghar walon ko shirk ki koi zarurat nahin . mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : dam jhaad, taaweez aur hubb ka amal (ye sab) shirk hain. mainey kaha : main eik din (ghar sey) nikli to falan shakhs ney mujhey dekh liya. meri jo aankh uski taraf thi, us sey pani bahney laga. jab main dam kawaati to pani ruk jata, jab main (dam kiraaey baghair) chhod deti to us sey pani bahney lagta. unhoney kaha : wo shetan tha, jab to uski marzi ka kaam karti thi, wo tujhey chhod deta, jab uski marzi key khilaf karti, wo teri aankh mein ungli maar deta. lekin agar to wo kaam karti jo Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kya tha to terey liye behtar hota aur tujhey zarur shifa mil jati. to apni aankh par pani key chheentey maar aur keh : ( أَذْهِبِ الْبَأْسَ رَبَّ النَّاسِ , وَاشْفِ أَنْتَ الشَّافِي , لَا شِفَاءَ إِلَّا شِفَاؤُكَ شِفَاءً لَا يُغَادِرُ سَقَمًا ) bimari door kar dey, aey logon key rab! shifa dey dey. to hi shifa deney wala hai. teri shifa key siwa koi shifa nahin, aisi shifa ata farma ke koi bimari baqi na rahey."
3531,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik shakhs key haath mein pital ka halqa (chhalla ya kada) dekha to farmaya : ye halqa kaisa hai? usney kaha : ye wahina ki bimari ki wajeh sey hai. aap ney farmaya : usey utaar dey, us sey teri kamzori mein izafa hi hoga."
3532,"Hazrat Umme Jundub (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey qurbani key din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney wadi key nashebi hissey mein khadey ho kar badey jamre par kankariyan maarin, phir wapis huye. qabila khasam ki khatoon aapkey peechey chal padi. uskey paas eik bacha tha jisey aaseb ki shikayat thi aur wo baat nahin karta tha. us khatoon ney arz ki : Allah key Rasool! ye mera beta hai aur merey ghar mein yehi baqi bacha hai aur usey aaseb hai, ye kalam nahin karta. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey paas thoda sa pani lao. pani laya gaya . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney haath dhoey aur kulli ki, phir (ye istemal kiya hua pani) usey dey diya aur farmaya : kuch pani usey pila dena, kuch uskey ooper dal dena, aur uskey liye Allah sey shifa ki dua karna. Umme Jundub (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : main us aurat sey mili aur kaha : is mein sey thoda sa (mutbarrak) pani mujhey bhi dey do. usney kaha : ye to us bimar key liye hai. Umme Jundub (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : eik saal baad us aurat sey meri mulaqat ho gaee to mainey us ladkey key barey mein poochha. usney kaha : wo sehat yaab ho gaya hai aur aisa aqlmand ho gaya hai jo (aam) logon ki tarah nahin (balke un sey badh kar aql mand ho gaya hai.)"
3533,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sab sey behtar dawaa Quran hai."
3534,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney do dhaariyon waley sanp ko qatl karney ka hukm diya kyonkey wo beenai zaya kar deta hai aur hamal ko nuqsan pahunchata hai. (dhaariyon waley sey) murad eik bura sanp hai."
3535,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : saanpon ko qatl karo, aur do lakeeron waley sanp ko aur dum katey sanp ko qatl kar do kyonkey ye beenai zaya kar detey hain aur hamal gira detey hain."
3536,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko achcha shagun lena pasand tha aur bad faali na pasand thi."
3537,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bimari ka mutaaddi hona koi chiz nahin, bad-faali kuch nahin, aur main achi faal ko pasand karta hun."
3538,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bad-faali shirk hai. aur hum mein sey har kisi ko koi na koi weham ho hi jata hai, lekin Allah Taala tawakkul ki wajeh sey usey dafa kar deta hai."
3539,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chhoot ki koi haqiqat nahin, bad shaguni ki koi haqiqat nahin, khopdi key ullu ki koi haqiqat nahin aur safar ki koi haqiqat nahin."
3540,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : na bimari chhut wali hoti hai, na bad-shagooni koi chiz hai aur na alu (الو) ki koi haqiqat hai. eik aadmi ney uth kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! eik khaarishi oont sey tamam oonton ko khaarish lag jati hai. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye taqdir hai, pehley oont ko kis ney khaarish lagai?"
3541,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bimar oonton wala tandurust oonton waley key sath (apney oonton ko) pani na pilaey."
3542,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik kodhi ka haath pakad kar apney sath piyaley mein dal diya (aur usey khaney mein shareek kar liya). phir farmaya : kha , Allah par aitimad kartey huye aur Allah par tawakkul kartey huye."
3543,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : juzaam key mareezon ko taktaki baandh kar na dekho."
3544,"Hazrat Amr (Rahimahullah) apney walid Hazrat Shareed Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : qabila Saqeef key wafad main eik majzoom aadmi tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey pegham bheja : wapis chala ja, hamney teri baiat ley li."
3545,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : qabila banu Zuraiq key eik Yahudi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par jadu kiya. us shakhs ka naam Labid bin Aasam tha. yahan tak key (ye haalat ho gaee ke) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye khayal hota ke aap falan kaam kar leingey, aur usey kar na saktey. eik din ya eik raat ki baat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney khub dua ki. uskey baad farmaya : Aaisha ! kya tujhey malum hai ke mainey Allah Taala sey jis kaam key barey mein rehnumai talab ki thi, Allah Taala ney uskey barey mein meri rehnumai farma di hai. merey paas do aadmi aaye. eik merey sar key qarib beth gaya aur doosra merey paon ki taraf beth gaya. merey sar key paas bethey huye ney merey paon key paas bethey huye sey , ya paon key paas bethey huye ney sar key paas bethey huye sey kaha : is shakhs ko kya takleef hai? doosrey ney kaha : is par jadu kiya gaya hai. usney kaha : jadu kis ney kiya? usney kaha : Labid bin Aasam ney. usney kaha : kis chiz mein? usney kaha kanghi mein, kanghi key sath utrey huye (sar key) baalon mein aur nar khajoor key khoshey key ghilaf mein. usney kaha : wo kahan hai? usney kaha : zii-arwaan key kunwen mein. Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) bayan farmaati hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney chand Sahaba key sath us kunwen par tashrif ley gaey. wapis aaney key baad farmaya : qism Allah ki ! Aaisha ! us kunwen ka pani aisa tha jaisey pani mein mahndi bhigoi gaee ho. aur khajoor key darkht aisey they jaisey shetanon key sar. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney usey jala kyon na diya? aap ney farmaya : nahin. mujhey to Allah Taala ney shifa dey di hai aur main nahin pasand karta ke logon mein iski wajeh sey shar phelaaun. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key hukm sey ye cheezen dafn kar di gaeen."
3546,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Ummul-mominin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney jo zahreeli bakri ka gosht khaya tha uski wajeh sey aap ko har saal takleef ho jati hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey uski wajeh sey jo musibat pahunchi hai, wo to us waqt meri taqdir mein likhi ja chuki thi jabke Adam (Alaihissalam) abhi mitti (ki shakal) mein they."
3547,"Hazrat Khaula binte Hakim (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar koi shakhs kisi manzil par theharte waqt ye dua padh ley to usey uskey kooch karney tak us manzil mein koi chiz takleef nahin pahunchaeygi (dua ye hai) : (أَعُوذُ بِكَلِمَاتِ اللَّهِ التَّامَّةِ مِنْ شَرِّ مَا خَلَقَ), ''main Allah ki paida ki hui har chiz key shar sey, Allah key kamil kalimaat ki panah mein aata hun.''"
3548,"Hazrat Usman bin Abi Al-Aas Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Taaif mein aamil muqarrar farmaya to mujhey namaz mein (pareshan-kun) khayalat aaney lagey yahan tak key mujhey ye bhi pata na chalta ke main namaz mein kya padh raha hun. jab mainey ye soorate-haal dekhi to main safar kar key Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney tajjub sey) farmaya : ibne-Abi Al-Aas ho? mainey kaha : ji haan, aey Allah key Rasool ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum aa kyon gaey? mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey namaz mein aisi soorate-haal pesh aati hai ke mujhey yad nahin rehta ke main namaz mein kya padh raha hun. aap ney farmaya : ye shetan ki taraf sey (shararat) hai. merey qarib aao. main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key qarib ho gaya aur panjon key bal beth gaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney merey seeney par haath maara aur merey munh mein thutkaaraa aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key dushman ! nikal ja. aap ney teen baar is tarah kiya. phir farmaya : apney kaam par chaley jao. Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : meri umr gawah hai ke uskey baad shetan ney mujhey pareshan nahin kiya."
3549,"Hazrat Abu-Laila Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas betha huwa tha ke eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mera bhai bimar hai. aap ney farmaya : terey bhai ko kya bimari laahiq hai? usney kaha : jinnon ki shikayat hai. aap ney farmaya : jao , usey merey paas lao. wo ja kar usey ley aaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us (mareez) ko apney samney bitha liya. mainey suna ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is par mandarja-zail aayaat padhin (aur dam kiya). Sura Fatiha , Sura Baqra ki pehli chaar aayaten, us (Sura Baqara) key darmiyan sey do aayaten, ( وَاِلٰهُكُمْ اِلٰهٌ وَّاحِد). (aayat : 163) aur Aayatul-kursi (aayat : 255) aur teen aayaten uskey aakhir sey (284 ta 486), Sura Aale-Imran sey eik aayat. ghaaliban ye aayat thi (شَهِدَ اللهُ أَنَّهُ لَااِلٰهَ إِلَّاهُو . .) (aayat : 18), Sura Aeraf ki eik aayat ( إِنَ رَبَّكُمُ الله . . ) (aayat : 54), Sura Mominoon ki eik aayat ( وَمَنْ يَدْعُ مَعَ اللَّهِ إِلَهًا آخَرَ لَا بُرْهَانَ لَهُ بِهِ . . ) (aayat : 117), Sura jin ki eik aayat ( وَأَنَّهُ تَعَالَى جَدُّ رَبِّنَا . . ) (aayat : 3), Sura Saaffaat ki pehli das aayaat, Sura Hashr ki aakhiri teen aayaat, Sura (قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ) mukammal aur muawwizatain (Sura Falaq aur Sura Naas mukammal), chunanche Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) sehat-yaab ho kar khada ho gaya, usey koi takleef na rahi."
